{"tid":1495381,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"92三罷宣傳嚴重不足！！","createTime":"2019-08-22T04:51:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T05:42:46.000Z","uid":48667,"like":74,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"37fd999f1d160e9abad0b7f76c675d5f1a13c22b","tid":1495381,"uid":48667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T04:51:28.000Z","msg":"過去既三罷有個道理好清楚<br />\n就係一定要及早開始宣傳同大幅度宣傳！！！<br />\n但熱門無人講, 討論post 又少<br />\n後續行動( 例如集會) 又無人講<br />\n咁點成功呀！？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kt1p96y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKt1p96y.jpg&h=2a0edc5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d6mQ5EX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd6mQ5EX.jpg&h=f4820e5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n文宣圖都好少呀！！推上熱門呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b0e7da916c719e2734fbbd9b490fee0f8a1bfe7","tid":1495381,"uid":55130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T04:53:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af7a9b85053bdf7acc1085e0f8cc5de4f4255b63","tid":1495381,"uid":35484,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T04:54:05.000Z","msg":"大家幾時先肯行動升級搞機場？<br />\n搞機場唔單只係搞到香港經濟，亦搞到全世界經濟<br />\n有機場巴絲亦指出，停飛一日全世界要2,3日善後<br />\n大家幾時先肯齊心搞呀？<br />\n唔係搞一日就算 係要成日搞<br />\n港共想攬炒唔志在香港蝕少少 但你覺得咁多受影響既外國公司想唔想蝕？<br />\n全世界陪葬既時候，你覺得啲大國會唔會出聲？<br />\n<br />\n重點係癱瘓機場交通，唔係塞爆機場入面<br />\n空管巴絲返唔到工，航班升降效率低左就會開始delay/cancel架喇"},{"pid":"afb521b0353587203a22f39a2b081222b0c37c6a","tid":1495381,"uid":48667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T04:56:40.000Z","msg":"推呀！！"},{"pid":"8e27f5be928b8f9385fac535c8a84187ac9e809f","tid":1495381,"uid":149008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T04:58:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/